GoldenEye:;

She glanced over her shoulder. "Oh that. It's nothing really. Just a 
bunch of Maximals fighting a bunch of Predacons.  Nothing unusual 
about that." She put her wing on the squirrels shoulder. "So you have 
no clue as to what you are or who you are eh? Well, let's see. No 
symbol. That means your undecided. That's good.  With no memory, that 
means your memory circuits got mixed up.  That I can help you with. 
But later on. For now, since you have no name, I shall have to give 
you one." She looked the animal over for a second. "How's about 
Tails. Yes, I think that will suit you nicely for now. Tails is what 
I name you." She transformed into bot mode.  She started to walk away 
when she noticed the squirrel didn't transform. "Well, transform and 
we shall get going before the battle lands on top of us."
